title: L'Oreal Paris True Match Super-Blendable Crayon Concealer, Fair/Light Neutral, 0.10 Ounces
description: Conceal it all, big to small. True match super-blendable crayon concealer offers customizable coverage from the tiniest of blemishes to larger areas of imperfections. description: Brushes set contains:1.Eyeliner Brush2.Lip Brush3.Eyebrow Brush4.Diagonal Brow Brush5.Eye Smudge BrushHow to clean makeup brushes:1. Run the bristles of brush under warm running water.2.
